milestones.description: Ranatunga has scored 19 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SL breaking de Silva's record
Mahanama and Athula Samarasekera's 128-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 101 between Wettimuny and Fernando
Kevin Arnott and Andy Flower's 85-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Dave Houghton and Andy Pycroft
Andy Waller and Andy Flower's 145-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 92 between Fletcher and Dave Houghton
Kevin Duers has conceded the most runs in an innings (72) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran's record of 65
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (13) for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton
Andy Waller and Andy Flower's 145-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 117 between Iain Butchart and Dave Houghton
